longBusinessSummary: Goliath Resources Limited engages in the acquisition and exploration of mineral properties in British Columbia, Canada. The company explores for gold, silver, copper, and molybdenum. It has an option to acquire 100% interests in Luckystrike property, which covers 31,511 hectares located in the Ominica and Skeena Mining Divisions in British Columbia; and the Golddigger property, which covers 23,858.51 hectares located to the southeast of Stewart. The company also holds interests in the Nelligan Project consisting of 391 mineral claims covering an area of 340 square kilometers situated in Quebec, Canada. Goliath Resources Limited is headquartered in Toronto, Canada.
